data.meta_description: PELICULAS - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document lists information about numerous films, including their genre, subgenre, director, release year, and cast. It provides titles, brief descriptions and production details for over 100 movies spanning various genres like action, comedy, western, horror and more. The listings include international films as well as Hollywood blockbusters and cult classics.
